node.text:
Some of my favourite clips from my part, Thank you @lego_city_river_man for capturing these moments and believing in my skating!🙌 
Link in bio to watch the full video😻 #skateboarding

node.text:
Still can’t believe this!! I want to thank all of you who follow me, show support, and like what I do. Ever since being a kid learning to kickflip I’ve always had the dream of turning pro. 
Thank you @hop_king for having my back! 
Keep being spectacular people🥰

Part is live!!🍻
Thank you @lego_city_river_man for sticking with me for hours on end to film this video, we’ve been working on this project for the past few months with @hop_king and we’re stoked to finally share this video, link in bio to watch hope you guys like it!🙌✨
